name: ArbiSwap
public_notice: According to reports we've received, the team has allegedly committed a rugpull by minting 1 billion fake tokens. We recommend that you conduct your own research (DYOR) and exercise caution before proceeding.
additional_notices: The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: ArbiSwap is one of the first DEX with an AMM on the Arbitrum Chain. ArbiSwap offers swapping of crypto for lowest fees and not only that, 100% fee is given back to holders of $ARBI making it the First total total decentralized exchange, where you can be the Traders, Liquidity Provider or part of the dex itself with $Arbi, it has something for everyone. From lowest fee to staking rewards to 100% protocol fees
